    "Finally, in spite of the fact that NTK-based analyses [Malladi et al., 2023, Jang et al., 2024] provide insight into the training dynamics and loss landscape of LoRA models, their conclusions are limited to the asymptotic (infinite-width) setting: they cannot necessarily be transferred to the real-world finite-width scenarios of interest in this work.",
